# üéß Listening Feature ‚Äî UI Mockups v2 (BA/QA/QC Analyzed)

> **Design System:** ui-ux-pro-max generated  
> **Style:** Dark OLED + Glassmorphism  
> **Colors:** Primary Blue `#2563EB` ¬∑ CTA Orange `#F97316`  
