## üó∫Ô∏è User Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["Dashboard"] --> B["Config Screen"]
    B --> C{"Mode?"}
    C -->|Podcast| D["Generating Screen"]
    C -->|Radio| E["Radio Mode"]
    D --> F["Player Full Mode"]
    E --> F
    F -->|Navigate away| G["Minimized Player"]
    F -->|Tap word| H["Dictionary Popup"]
    F -->|Gyroscope| I["Pocket Mode"]
    F -->|Long press| J["Bookmark saved"]
    B -->|Settings icon| K["TTS Settings Sheet"]
    B -->|Custom icon| L["Custom Scenarios"]
    B -->|Audio playing| M["Confirm Dialog"]
    G -->|Tap| F
    A -->|First time| N["Walkthrough Tour"]
    J --> O["Bookmarks & Vocabulary"]
```

