## Design System Summary

| Token | Value |
|-------|-------|
| Primary | `#2563EB` (Blue) |
| CTA | `#F97316` (Orange) |
| Background | `#000000` (OLED Black) |
| Surface | `#121212` |
| Card | `rgba(255,255,255,0.05)` + blur |
| Border | `rgba(255,255,255,0.08)` |
| Text | `#FAFAFA` |
| Secondary text | `#6E6E6E` |
| Typography | DM Sans 400/500/700 |
| Icons | Lucide React Native |
| Radius | 16px cards, 24px sheets |
| Accessibility | WCAG AAA on text |
